### Folder to Archive

~~~ .php
Folder::open('.\path\to\folder')->packAs('foo.zip');
~~~

### Files to Archive

~~~ .php
File::open([
    '.\path\to\file.css' => 'css\asset.css',
    '.\path\to\file.js' => 'js\asset.js',
    '.\path\to\file.html' => 'index.html'
])->packAs('foo.zip');
~~~

### Extract Package

~~~ .php
Package::open('.\path\to\file.zip')->extract();
~~~

